    emmo:elucidation """A ban is a logarithmic unit which measures information or entropy, based on base 10 logarithms and powers of 10, rather than the powers of 2 and base 2 logarithms which define the bit. One ban is approximately 3.32 (log₂ 10) bits.

-- QUDT"""@en ;
