    emmo:elucidation """The `fermi`, or `femtometer` (other spelling femtometre, symbol fm) is an SI unit of length equal to 10⁻¹⁵ metre. This distance is often encountered in nuclear physics as a characteristic of this scale. The symbol for the fermi is also fm.

