    skos:prefLabel "JoulePerQuarticMetre"@en ;
    emmo:elucidation """`Joule Per Quartic Meter` (J/m⁴) is a unit for the spectral concentration of radiant energy density (in terms of wavelength), or the spectral radiant energy density (in terms of wave length). This unit is commonly used in the SI unit system.

-- QUDT"""@en ;
