    skos:altLabel "Pascal Second Per Metre"@en ;
    skos:prefLabel "PascalSecondPerMetre"@en ;
    emmo:EMMO_8189b42e_0995_423a_a26c_51168b27c3cf 1e+00 ;
    emmo:EMMO_d088a3cb_d3e3_4eb2_9897_00aef0cb00cd 0e+00 ;
    emmo:elucidation """Pascal Second Per Meter (Pa-s/m) is a unit in the category of Specific acoustic impedance. It is also known as pascal-second/meter. Pascal Second Per Meter has a dimension of ML²T⁻¹ where M is mass, L is length, and T is time. It essentially the same as the corresponding standard SI unit kg/m2· s.

-- QUDT"""@en ;
