    emmo:EMMO_d088a3cb_d3e3_4eb2_9897_00aef0cb00cd 0e+00 ;
    emmo:elucidation """Square Meter Per Mole (m2/mol) is a unit in the category of Specific Area. It is also known as square meters per mole, square metre per per, square metres per per, square meter/per, square metre/per. This unit is commonly used in the SI unit system. Square Meter Per Mole (m2/mol) has a dimension of M-1L2 where M is mass, and L is length. This unit is the standard SI unit in this category.

-- QUDT"""@en ;
