    emmo:elucidation "Assigns a quantifiable uncertainty to an objective property through a well-defined procecure."@en ;
    emmo:note "Since measurement uncertainty is a subclass of objective property, this relation can also describe the uncertainty of an measurement uncertainty."@en .

