    emmo:elucidation "Short enlightening explanation aimed to facilitate the user in drawing the connection (interpretation) between a OWL entity and the real world object(s) for which it stands."@en ;
    emmo:note "An elucidation should address the real world entities using the concepts introduced by the conceptualisation annotation."@en .

